{"tid":1515185,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"橙新聞係聯合出版集團旗下子公司","createTime":"2019-08-29T04:45:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:50:24.000Z","uid":60545,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"75147f65c50c1f73d3c70c6b7f260a5a396f1945","tid":1515185,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:45:53.000Z","msg":"而聯合出版集團係咩我相信大家知啦？<br />\n佢係中聯辦控制丶全資擁有嘛<br />\n<br />\n而除咗橙新聞之外<br />\n大公文滙丶商報丶HKG報丶點新聞丶三中商(三聯丶中華丶商務)都係佢哋嘅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/聯合出版集團\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%87%BA%E7%89%88%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRkZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=6b6a0a2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/聯合出版集團</a>"},{"pid":"a924383ff868feed817ad87bbc78b07987feced1","tid":1515185,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b804cecfe3bcaf6716cd18d952faa886b5071f25","tid":1515185,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c68d2fbecfac86358739de85abe2e0b667cd58","tid":1515185,"uid":260262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:48:24.000Z","msg":"份份都藍到發黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06377dde7af142c0a50f76727d5245701aeae473","tid":1515185,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e94e1f62cef7b6e99223580c6731cce03e8fadb","tid":1515185,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:51:37.000Z","msg":"原來有人唔知"},{"pid":"9d786dab4cc08dc34fd53cf0f8387fba65746f4c","tid":1515185,"uid":50904,"